  "messages": [
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "How did the appointment go? Thinking of you. ❤️",
    "time": "2026-05-11T18:26:25"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus Webb",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Did you ever get a hold of that contact at the boutique? Need a second pair of eyes on this memo before it goes to Anika.",
    "time": "2026-05-12T18:53:24"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Dinner at Ambar? I can grab a reservation if you're off shift by 7.",
    "time": "2026-05-14T18:33:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Holloway HQ",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just saw the update on Dad's physical therapy. Sending love from VA. Miss you guys.",
    "time": "2026-05-17T20:05:01"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus Webb",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Hey man, you still on for squash at Sport&Health this Friday? Need to work on my backhand before the weekend.",
    "time": "2026-05-19T18:38:52"
   },
   {
    "with": "Peggy Holloway",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Hi honey, just checking in. Your father had a bit of a rough morning, but he's resting now. Hope work isn't too stressful. Love you!",
    "time": "2026-05-23T11:35:52"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus Webb",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Man, just got a text from my mom. Dad's struggling again. I feel like a total prick for being stuck in DC while everything's going sideways in Cincy. Can't focus on this memo at all.",
    "time": "2026-05-23T14:08:21"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus Webb",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Squash Friday? 5:30?",
    "time": "2026-05-26T18:41:36"
   },
   {
    "with": "J.R.",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Need to sync on that memo update",
    "time": "2026-05-28T16:51:44"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus Webb",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Rough week, man. Call later?",
    "time": "2026-05-29T22:16:46"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus Webb",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Man, if I don't wrap this regional assessment by midnight I'm actually going to lose it. This NSC review pressure is getting absurd. Need a drink soon.",
    "time": "2026-06-01T18:47:46"
   },
   {
    "with": "Emily",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Hey, just a heads up, Dad's tremors were pretty bad this morning. Mom's really stressed. Call me when you can?",
    "time": "2026-06-02T10:18:52"
   },
   {
    "with": "Sarah",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Thinking of you. Hope the shift isn't too brutal tonight. ❤️",
    "time": "2026-06-02T19:41:27"
   }
